commentary: Mohammed Shami to Taylor, OUT nudges it straight to the keeper. But he's reviewed it. Bat was close to pad and possibly connected with the pad at the same time as he got this edge. Because there's no real reason to review this otherwise. It's at a length, just outside off. Thick edge straight to the keeper as he tried to guide it down to third man. New Zealand lose their review. Falls short of the hunded by seven runs, and now NZ have 29 balls with Bracewell and the tail.
